reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Life saver protection.
reviews.reviewText: The YMHML 8 Pack Screen Protector for Apple Watch is awesome! Easy to put on and protects my watch screen perfectly. Saved me so much money from hits and scratches. If you want to keep your Apple Watch safe, these protectors are a must-have. Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: It comes with all the tools and easy-to-follow instructions to slap it on your watch. I didn't bother with the instructions and still got it done, and I'm pretty stoked with how it turned out. I'm always banging my watch around, and this thing seems to be doing a solid job keeping it safe. Simple fix, but it works!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Decent for the price
reviews.reviewText: The protectors are pretty soft and don’t hold up great to wear and tear, but they do protect the screen well. You might find yourself replacing the protector more often than you’d like.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Awesome screen protectors
reviews.reviewText: It took me several tries to get this on properly (definitely watch the YouTube video for instructions) but once I did. It is beautiful and I can barely tell it’s there. My watch has a decent size case on it, which normally peels screen protectors of within a day of wearing. I’ve been wearing my watch with both the screen protector and a case during heavy work as a mechanic, for 3-4 weeks, and the first one I successfully installed is still installed, hasn’t peeled/bubbles, and only has 1 minor surface scratch. Definitely try these

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not a really good fit
reviews.reviewText: I ordered these screen protectors because my watch face was slightly scratched and these were shown to help hide scratches. Let me say that they do work well in that regard. And as long as I wear these without any bumpers or kind of protective guard they stay on pretty good. However, I tried to place these on and then use my bumper with my watch band and even though the bumper should’ve let me do this they kept peeling off on the edges. I tried several times and they wouldn’t stay. My other issue is that they are a bit complicated to apply. There’s no doubt that you MUST watch the installation video, but even then it’s pretty confusing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: At first I thought these would break and scratch easily but once I used it for a while I was shocked at how well they work. The amount of times I’ve bumped my watch and haven’t gotten a scratch is crazy. They’re slim so they aren’t so noticeable. I highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I cracked my previous Apple Watch so I ordered these to prevent that! Definitely watch the video to see how to install because it’s a bit tricky but then goes on easy as pie. Can’t even tell it’s there and I love that it comes with so many extras.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not very durable but ok
reviews.reviewText: The instructions and materials provided to install this are really great. I installed it with no bubbles or dust underneath. It is smooth and shiny. Within the first weeks of having on the screen protector, it split at two of the rounded edges and dust got under and I had to change it out, thankfully the pack comes with more.So far it is holding up. Lost one star for the lack of durability.
